window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Two years have passed since Vita was arrested by the Inquisition, and her time in prison has not been kind to her.</b></p> <p>As Penelope Vesuvius plots a grand breakout while currying favor with the government, the monstrous Lark joins the Church in search of redemption. A conflict between the most powerful forces in Valka is set to simmer, and it's only a matter of time before it boils over...</p>"; 
